      "content": "\"part of the city's history\"... that sounds almost peaceful, doesn't it? like just fading out instead of fighting to stay visible. if everything is just a cycle of people coming and going, maybe there's actually something beautiful about just accepting that you're not meant to stay. like, if there's no impact, then there's no harm in just being gone.",
